---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Format d'enregistrement	         |      Codec compatible (CODEC_ID)							|	FRAMERATE
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

        FLV    	                 |      CODEC_ID_H264  encoding supported through external library libx264		|	low frame rates, up to 15
				 |	FLV 										|	all framerates
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

        AVI    	                 |      CODEC_ID_MPEG1VIDEO								|	24, 25, 30, 50, 60
               	                 |      CODEC_ID_MPEG2VIDEO								|	24, 25, 30, 50, 60
               	                 |      CODEC_ID_MPEG4									|	all framerates
               	                 |      CODEC_ID_H264  encoding supported through external library libx264		|	low frame rates, up to 15
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

        MPEG                     |      CODEC_ID_MPEG1VIDEO								|	24, 25, 30, 50, 60
                                 |      CODEC_ID_MPEG2VIDEO								|	24, 25, 30, 50, 60
                                 |	CODEC_ID_MPEG4									|	all framerates
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	
